text: Sisyracera contortilinealis is a moth in the family Crambidae. It is found on Puerto Rico,Aaron Cavosie's Moths of Puerto Rico Dominica, Grenada, Jamaica, Cuba and in Guyana. ==References== Category:Moths described in 1895 Category:Pyraustinae Category:Moths of the Caribbean Category:Moths of South America
title: Sisyracera contortilinealis
